lead_paragraph: Thorbjorn Olesen won the Turkish Airlines Open on Sunday, securing the biggest payday of his career after nearly throwing away the seven-shot lead he took into the final round.

headline.print_headline: Olesen Wins Turkish Airlines Open for Biggest Career Payday
